fourier.txt

Fourier's diffusion spread equation
dT/dt = a d^2T/dx^2

E = mCT
dE = mCdT

E = Wt = QSt
dE =dQ S dt

mCdT = dQ S dt

dT/dt = dQ S/(mC) = dQ S/(p S dx C) = dQ / (p dx C) = 1/pC dQ/dx

Fourier's law
dQ = -k dT/dx

dT/dt = 1/pC d/dx (-k dT/dx)
      = 1/pC d^2/dx^2 (-k dT)
      = -k/pC d^2/dx^2 T

a = -k/pC

therefore dT/dt = a d^2T/dx^2
